    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>座会反击的活体岛屿</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/4005c982d880b2ccfe8eb2e6abac9439.poster.avif?t=1769338584\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/4005c982d880b2ccfe8eb2e6abac9439.webm?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/4005c982d880b2ccfe8eb2e6abac9439.mp4?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿的每一处都在遭受围攻。水源在火山灰中干涸，火焰毫无预警地蔓延，大地在你脚下震颤。这是一款城市建造游戏，你必须不断争夺对这个不可预测世界的控制权。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>顺应变化，灵活应对</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/8763f0187d6a180266c1a09780d44c16.poster.avif?t=1769338584\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/8763f0187d6a180266c1a09780d44c16.webm?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/8763f0187d6a180266c1a09780d44c16.mp4?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座始终活跃的火山岛上，大自然本身就是你最大的敌人。火球、地震与火山灰不断威胁你的生存。打造一个坚韧的定居点不仅需要规划，更需要适应混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>崛起、崩塌、重建</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/463daadfca78d01e19b9d280b00d5b2b.poster.avif?t=1769338584\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/463daadfca78d01e19b9d280b00d5b2b.webm?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/463daadfca78d01e19b9d280b00d5b2b.mp4?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造一个人类与魔像协同工作的社会。魔像是为岛屿残酷环境而生的古老、不知疲倦的构造体。它们协助劳作，抵御环境威胁，成为你不断扩张的定居点的核心支柱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让火山沉寂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/926db081faae3cdad78842afe46a6569.poster.avif?t=1769338584\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/926db081faae3cdad78842afe46a6569.webm?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294080/extras/926db081faae3cdad78842afe46a6569.mp4?t=1769338584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地表之下，终极挑战正等待着你。在一切被吞噬之前阻止火山爆发。这场最终对决将考验你的系统运作能力，以及人民的意志与决心。</p>",
